          "type": "text",
          "text": "1. Overview"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "dbo.NewMeters_IT",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " table is designed to store information related to utility meters. It captures details about the utility company, account numbers, meter numbers, and the date when the meter became effective. This table is part of a larger database system used by utility companies to manage and track meter installations and their associated accounts."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
