      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The table structure is relatively simple, consisting of only four columns with no apparent indexes, primary keys, or foreign keys defined. The absence of these elements shows a low complexity level in terms of structure and relationships."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
